  "title": "Customer Service Associate – Order & Sales Support (Maternity Cover) | Tuas - 5 days [0580]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Maternity Cover - Feb to May </li><li>Working hour : 8.30am-6pm ( Mon - Fri )</li><li>Salary : $2500-$3000</li><li>Location : Tuas</li></ul><p><strong>Job scope :</strong></p><p><em><strong>Sales Order Processing (The following to be carried out on a timely basis):</strong></em></p><ul><li>Receive and enter orders into the system, acknowledge customers’ P.O.s on time</li><li>For new customers, arrange with customer to complete credit application form, establish custom exemption status and freight arrangements where applicable.</li><li>Update weekly delivery schedule & update open order items that already shipped.</li><li>Update order quantities on MS/MRP.</li><li>Liaise with customers on current and forecast orders, monitor status of ordering, inventory and outstanding accounts.</li><li>Prepare shipping documentation, invoices, etc. for goods dispatch/delivery amendment and cancellation.</li><li>Liaise with Production, Planning, Purchasing and Warehouse to ensure order fulfilled as per requirements e.g. timely delivery.</li><li>Perform the above for sample requests where applicable.</li><li>Any other tasks related to order fulfillment (including unique requests).</li></ul><p><em><strong>Customer Service:</strong></em></p><ul><li>Handle customer enquiries and maintain good customer relations.</li><li>Respond to customer complaints and forward to QA for investigation.</li><li>To follow with QA to close complaints.</li><li>Other related customer service work.</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
